OL,3,CApologies after mural of poet Benjamin
OL,4,CZephaniah painted over in error
OL,6,FA mural depicting the Birmingham poet
OL,7,Fand campaigner
OL,9,FThe colourful painting was on the wall
OL,10,Fof an underpass in the Hockley area of
OL,12,FCouncil contractors Kier removed it -
OL,13,Fbecause it was not covered by a
OL,14,Fprotection order.
OL,16,FIt was made in tribute to the poet and
OL,17,Factivist who died last December after
OL,18,Fbeing diagnosed with a brain tumour.
