OL,3,CApologies after mural of poet Benjamin
OL,4,CZephaniah painted over in error
OL,6,FThe company has now apologised for
OL,7,Ftheir actions and said it will work
OL,8,Fwith the artist to recreate the art
OL,9,Fwork, including providing materials.
OL,11,FThe city council said that contractors
OL,12,Fworking for Kier regularly remove
OL,13,Fgraffiti or paintings on subway walls.
OL,14,FThey are supposed to leave artwork
OL,15,Fwithin the underpass area as there is
OL,16,Fa protection order in place, but the
OL,17,Forder fails to include the outside
OL,18,Fwalls - where this painting was.
