OL,3,CApologies after mural of poet Benjamin
OL,4,CZephaniah painted over in error
OL,6,FThey said, "We confirm that we will be
OL,7,Fseeking to add this particular section
OL,8,Fof the Hockley subway system to the
OL,9,Fprotection order, to further mitigate
OL,10,Fagainst this happening again in
OL,11,Ffuture."
OL,13,FA Kier spokesperson said: "We
OL,14,Fapologise for any hurt or distress we
OL,15,Fhave caused by painting over this
OL,16,Fmural, crews were carrying out their
OL,17,Fstandard duties and there was no ill-
OL,18,Fintent, but we accept the upset caused
OL,19,Fby our actions.
